I"§<h3 id="storing-git-username-and-password-for-pushing-without-entering-username-and-password">Storing git username and password for pushing without entering username and password</h3>

<p>In any directory (non .git)</p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">$ git config --global credential.helper cache</code></p>

<p>In a repository (To enable for this repository)</p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">$ git config credential.helper cache</code></p>

<p>Then</p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">$ git push</code></p>

<p>Enter username and password and after that, all pushes will not require you to enter your password.</p>

